Skill: Bash        Timer: Damage       GL: 15    Cost: 25%
A basic fighter attack skill. You wind up with all your strength and bash
your enemy on the head.

You will be much more effective if you use a weapon (and one that would
make sense to use when bashing someone over the head helps!), otherwise you 
will use your bare hands.

When bashing a target you can sometimes hit them hard enough that it
decreases their ability to fight back effectively.

Syntax is: bash <target>
